text: Ilaka KisKishoreganj is a Hindi film directed by the husband-wife duo of J Nutan-Pankaj. The film has been produced under the banners of Ma Devdi Motion Pictures, Tej World Entertainment, Daksh World Entertainment and Anukriti Entertainment Private Ltd. The cast includes Rohit RK, Shikha Swarup, Rupesh Kumar Charan Pahari, Deepak Lohar, Lilawati, and Anand Kumar. ==Cast== *Rohit RK *Shikha Swaroop * Rupesh Kumar Charan Pahari *Deepak Lohar *Lilawati *Anand Kumar ==References== ==External links== * Category:Indian films
